  "about": "Onetwo is a music production house specialised in bespoke music for film. Our team of producers are highly trained multi-instrumentalist composers with many years of experience in sound engineering, who always deliver impactful solutions to our clients. We are housed in a modular studio space in Athens, Greece, built in 2018, containing a combination of legendary analog recording equipment as well as state-of-the-art contemporary digital interfaces and instruments, giving us the ability to produce everything in-house. We invite you to navigate our page and see for yourselves. Our promise is simple: The perfect soundtrack to your brand.",
